        <Description>SDK for OPC Unified Architecture (OPC UA) server has uncaught exception when a socket is blocked for writing but the server tries to send an error</Description>
        <Link>https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2023-41151</Link>
      </Observed_Example>
      <Observed_Example>
        <Reference>CVE-2023-21087</Reference>
        <Description>Java code in a smartphone OS can encounter a "boot loop" due to an uncaught exception</Description>
        <Link>https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2023-21087</Link>
      </Observed_Example>
     </Observed_Examples>
